### orderservice — REST Client
### 使用 Event Sourcing + EventStoreDB (每次操作都是一个 event，聚合状态由事件流回放而来)
### 用法：光标放到 ### 下的请求块，点 "Send Request"

@host = http://localhost:8000
@base = {{host}}/api/v1

########################################
# Orders
########################################

### 列出所有 orders（分页）
GET {{base}}/orders?page=1&size=20&orderBy=createdAt
Accept: application/json


### 创建一个 order
# @name createOrder
POST {{base}}/orders
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountEmail": "alice@example.com",
  "deliveryAddress": "221B Baker Street, London",
  "deliveryTime": "2026-07-20T12:00:00Z",
  "shopItems": [
    {
      "title": "Pizza Margherita",
      "description": "Classic tomato + mozzarella",
      "quantity": 2,
      "price": 12.5
    },
    {
      "title": "Coke",
      "description": "330ml can",
      "quantity": 1,
      "price": 2.0
    }
  ]
}


### 从响应里取出 orderId
@orderId = {{createOrder.response.body.Id}}


### 按 id 查询（内部通过事件流回放得到当前状态）
GET {{base}}/orders/{{orderId}}
Accept: application/json


########################################
# 观察 event sourcing 的地方：
# EventStoreDB UI: http://localhost:2113  (admin/changeit)
#   在 Streams 里找  order-{orderId}  之类的 stream，能看到每一步 event
# Swagger UI:      http://localhost:8000/swagger/index.html
# Jaeger (trace):  http://localhost:16686
########################################
